The paper deals with communication over quantum channels, which is a topic that falls under both information theory (cs.IT) and quantum physics (cs.QUANT-PH). The paper also involves the study of capacity-distortion regions, which is a topic in control theory and systems engineering (cs.SY). The use of regularization techniques is also mentioned, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.MM) and optimization (cs.LG).
